name: WWUD-CS
tagline: What would you do site in C#
body:
# WWUD-CS

**WWUD-CS **is an ASP.net MVC5 site written in C# using Entity Framework 6. I'm using this site as a testing ground for me to learn asp.net and mvc technologies. 

The **_Development_** branch is my working branch and will change constantly. It will always contain the latest code but may be broken at any given time.

The **_Master_** branch will be updated periodically from development.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
